name: NanoMeter Bitcoin
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
NMBTC specifically has the potential to be a DeFi 2.0 leader, and we welcome and embrace all viewpoints and are committed to building the best community for cryptocurrency.
NMBTC will create a physical mine industry in the future, empower NMBTC, and will combine online liquidity mining to realize online and offline integration.
